PRETORIA - The Minister of Social Development Bathabile Dlamini, will brief members of the media on progress made regarding the institutionalisation of the social grants payment system beyond 31 March 2017.The current contract with Cash Paymaster Services expires at the end of this month.The minister said she and the South African Social Security Agency (SASSA) would like to reassure beneficiaries that they will get their social grants on 1 April 2017. eNCA